From the given problem data, the relevant line item is:

| Account             | Initial_amount | Initial_date  | End_amount   | End_date    |
|---------------------|----------------|---------------|--------------|-------------|
| Accounts Receivable  | 0.00           | 2023-12-31    | 2902136.39   | 2024-02-05  |

No other account fits the description as clearly as Accounts Receivable.

Thus, the initial value is 0.00 and the end value is 2902136.39.
